race.description: Racing Again Melbourne Cup Tue 4th Nov Hcp (Bm60)
race.comment: WHATTA WHITT (6) is absolutely flying and can make it three on the bounce. Was dominant again last start when on pace and putting a decent space on his rivals. Not a great deal tougher this time, everything points to another winning performance. RICH DIVINITY (2) rarely runs a bad race and gets a lovely setup on his home deck. Doesn't win often but his consistency makes him a key player. RAETIHI (1) has been racing well and maps to advantage. Could take some reeling in if left alone in front. HELL OF A TRIP (4) is honest and the booking of Wiggins looks significant. ANSWERING (3) should improve with that run under his belt and is among the chances.
